modules.description: This module builds and manipulates Content Identifier (CID) values using a specified multihash implementation. It supports creating CIDs from version, base encoding, codec, and hash components, parsing CIDs from strings or binary buffers, and converting them back to strings or structured binary data. Use cases include working with IPFS or Filecoin content identifiers, verifying CID components, and handling multibase-encoded data.
